    "headline": "Is the Stock Market Open Today? Here Are the Trading Hours for Good Friday.",
    "summary": "Here’s what to know about trading hours for Good Friday.  The New York Stock Exchange and the Nasdaq Stock Market will both be closed on Friday.  Similarly, over-the-counter markets, the Cboe Futures Exchange, and the CME Globex trading platform will be shut on Friday, as will the bond market, which closed early at 2 p.m. on Thursday.",
